          <div class="station-info">
            <h4>North Side Station (FREE)</h4>
            <p>North Shore. Park nearby and ride to Wood Street for free.</p>
            <div class="station-links">
              <a href="/assets/2026-travel-assistance/north-side-map.jpeg" target="_blank">Area map</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="station-block">
          <a href="/assets/2026-travel-assistance/station-square-entrance.jpeg" target="_blank" class="station-thumb">
            <img src="/assets/2026-travel-assistance/station-square-entrance.jpeg" alt="Station Square entrance" />
          </a>
          <div class="station-info">
            <h4>Station Square — $2.75 (free as bus transfer)</h4>
            <p>South of downtown. Pay with the <a href="https://www.rideprt.org/fares-and-passes/mobileticket/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong>Ready2Ride</strong></a> app or at the station. If you're transferring from a bus and paid with the app or ConnectCard, the T ride is included.</p>
            <div class="station-links">
              <a href="/assets/2026-travel-assistance/station-square-map.jpeg" target="_blank">Area map</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="station-block">
          <a href="/assets/2026-travel-assistance/wood-street-station-entrance.jpeg" target="_blank" class="station-thumb">
            <img src="/assets/2026-travel-assistance/wood-street-station-entrance.jpeg" alt="Wood Street Station entrance" />
          </a>
          <div class="station-info">
            <h4>Wood Street Station (Your Destination)</h4>
            <p>Get off here—it's a 1-minute walk to the Harris Theater.</p>
